OL,3,CIsle of Man set to take historic step
OL,4,Ccloser to legalising assisted dying
OL,6,FFinal amendments to the Assisted Dying
OL,7,FBill are going to be debated in the
OL,8,FManx Parliament on Tuesday 25
OL,9,FFebruary, before it becomes law in the
OL,10,FIsle of Man.
OL,12,FProtestors are expected to gather
OL,13,Foutside of Tynwald as members of the
OL,14,FHouse of Keys make the decision.
OL,16,FThe amendments include training for
OL,17,Fhealthcare professionals and
OL,18,Fpsychiatrist referrals to ensure it is
OL,19,Fthe person's own decision and that it
OL,20,Fis made when they are in the right
OL,21,Fstate of mind to do so.
