OL,3,CIsle of Man set to take historic step
OL,4,Ccloser to legalising assisted dying
OL,6,FIf passed, terminally ill residents
OL,7,Fwould have access to assisted dying as
OL,8,Fearly as 2027.
OL,10,FMembers of the Legislative Council
OL,11,F(MLCs) voted overwhelmingly for the
OL,12,Fchange.
OL,14,FThe debate now returns to the lower
OL,15,Fchamber of Tynwald, for the 24 members
OL,16,Fof the House of Keys (MHKs) to have a
OL,17,Ffinal say on whether it should be
OL,18,Fintroduced.
OL,20,FMLCs made the following changes, to be
OL,21,Fvoted on by MHKs:
