OL,3,CIsle of Man set to take historic step
OL,4,Ccloser to legalising assisted dying
OL,6,FIf all clauses and amendments are
OL,7,Fagreed by both chambers in Tynwald,
OL,8,Fthe Assisted Dying Bill will be sent
OL,9,Ffor Royal Assent.
OL,11,FAn implementation period would then
OL,12,Ffollow, before assisted dying would
OL,13,Fbecome available to terminally ill
OL,14,Fresidents.
OL,16,FThe debate in Tynwald comes after a
OL,17,Fmajority of MPs in Westminster voted
OL,18,Fto back Kim Leadbeater MP's Terminally
OL,19,FIll Adults (End of Life) Bill at its
OL,20,FSecond Reading in November.
