OL,3,CIsle of Man set to take historic step
OL,4,Ccloser to legalising assisted dying
OL,6,FThe Westminster Bill would enable
OL,7,Fterminally ill, mentally competent
OL,8,Fadults, with a prognosis of six months
OL,9,For less, to have the choice of an
OL,10,Fassisted death.
OL,12,FIt has now entered its Committee
OL,13,FStage, where a group of cross-party
OL,14,FMPs, will hear expert evidence,
OL,15,Fscrutinise the Bill line-by-line and
OL,16,Fpropose amendments.
OL,18,FWhat is assisted dying?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
